SIMPLE: peanut_gallery
RECORDS: 1

==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Peanut gallery
<hw>Pea"nut gal"ler*y</hw>. <sn>1.</sn> <def>The cheapest seats in a
theater, being typically those farthest from the stage, as in the
uppermost balcony.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>PJC</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>In a television show for children, the section where
visiting children sit as guests during the performance.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>PJC</source>]</p>

<p><sn>3.</sn> <specif>Hence:</specif> <def>Any group of children, or
the children in a group of people; <as>as, let's have no noise from the
<ex>peanut gallery</ex></as>.</def> <mark>[Colloq.]</mark> ⟦br⟧
[<source>PJC</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Pear</ent>⟦br⟧
